has died","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 10, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: Abu Bakr, may Allah be pleased with him, went to the door of the mosque when he heard the news of the passing of the Prophet. Abu Bakr said, \u201cTo proceed: Whoever among you worships Muhammad, peace and blessings be upon him, then Muhammad has died. Whoever\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36569,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/06\/03\/jihad-no-war-combat-killing\/","url_meta":{"origin":33695,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Hajj: Jihad for women without fighting","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 3, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, is jihad a duty upon women?\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cYes, jihad is a duty upon them in which there is no fighting: the Hajj and 'Umrah pilgrimages.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 2901 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8411,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/16\/allah-reveals-death-surah-al-nasr\/","url_meta":{"origin":33695,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Death: Allah reveals to the Prophet his end is near","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 16, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Razin reported: Umar, may Allah be pleased with him, asked Ibn Abbas about th